#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:5
msgid "Hook Modifier"
msgstr "钩挂修改器"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:7
msgid ""
"The *Hook* modifier is used to deform a *Mesh*, *Curve* or *Lattice* using "
"another object (usually an *Empty* or a *Bone* but it can be any object)."
msgstr ""
"挂钩修改器用其他物体（通常是 *空物体* 或 *骨骼*，但可以用任何物体）来变形 *网格"
"* 、*曲线* 或 *晶格* 。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:10
msgid ""
"As an object specified as hook moves, it pulls vertices or control points from "
"the geometry with it. You can think of it as animated :doc:`Proportional "
"Editing </scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/proportional_edit>`."
msgstr ""
"当指定为挂钩的物体移动时，它会从几何体中拉出顶点或控制点。你可以把它想象成 :"
"doc:`衰减编辑 </scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/"
"proportional_edit>` 。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:14
msgid ""
"While hooks do not give you the fine control over vertices movement that shape "
"keys do, they have the advantage that you can select vertices directly for "
"manipulation."
msgstr ""
"虽然钩子不能像形状键那样很好地控制顶点的移动，但它们的优势是可以直接选择顶点进"
"行操作。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:17
msgid ""
"To assign selected vertices (in Edit Mode) you can use the *Assign* button on "
"the modifier panel or use the :ref:`Add Hook <bpy.ops.object.hook_add_selob>` "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"使用修改器面板的 *指定* 按钮或 :ref:`添加挂钩 <bpy.ops.object.hook_add_selob>` "
"菜单指定选中的顶点 (编辑模式下)。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:22
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:27
msgid "The Hook modifier."
msgstr "钩挂修改器。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:29
msgid "Object"
msgstr "物体"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:30
msgid "The name of the object to hook vertices to."
msgstr "钩挂顶点的物体的名字。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:34
msgid "Vertex Group"
msgstr "顶点组"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:32
msgid "Allows you to define the influence per vertex."
msgstr "允许你对每个顶点设定影响程度。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:34
msgid "Useful when you want something other than a spherical field of influence."
msgstr "当你不是想要一个球型影响域时，它很有用。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:36
msgid "Radius"
msgstr "半径"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:37
msgid "The size of the hooks influence."
msgstr "钩挂作用的范围。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:41
msgid "Strength"
msgstr "强度"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:39
msgid ""
"Adjust this hooks influence on the vertices, were (0.0 to 1.0) (no change to "
"fully follows the hook)."
msgstr "调整这个挂钩对顶点的影响，从（0.0到1.0）（使顶点没有改变完全跟随钩子）。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:41
msgid ""
"Since multiple hooks can work on the same vertices, you can weight the "
"influence of a hook using this property."
msgstr ""
"由于多个挂钩操作可作用在同一个顶点上，你可以用这个属性来加权一个挂钩操作的影响"
"力。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:44
msgid "Falloff Type"
msgstr "衰减类型"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:44
msgid ""
"This can be used to adjust the kind of influence curve that the hook has on "
"the mesh. You can also define a custom curve to get a much higher level of "
"control."
msgstr ""
"这可以用来调整挂钩对网格的影响曲线。您还可以定义自定义曲线来获得更高级别的控"
"制。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:50
msgid "Uniform Falloff"
msgstr "均匀衰减"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:47
msgid ""
"This setting is useful when using hooks on scaled objects, especially in cases "
"where non-uniform scale would stretch the result of the hook."
msgstr ""
"当在缩放对象上使用钩挂时，此设置非常有用，特别是在非均匀缩放会拉伸钩挂结果的情"
"况下。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:50
msgid ""
"This is especially useful for lattices, where it is common to use non-uniform "
"scaling."
msgstr "该项对晶格非常有用，这在使用非均匀缩放是很常见。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:52
msgid "The following settings are only available in Edit Mode:"
msgstr "以下设置仅在编辑模式可用："

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:54
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "重置"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:55
msgid "Recalculate and clear the offset transform of the hook."
msgstr "重新计算，并清除钩挂操作的偏移变换。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:57
msgid "Recenter"
msgstr "重新指定中心"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:57
msgid "Set the hook center to the 3D cursor position."
msgstr "设置挂钩中心为3D光标的位置。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:59
msgid "Select"
msgstr "选择"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:60
msgid "Select the vertices affected by this hook."
msgstr "选择受该挂钩影响的顶点。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:62
msgid "Assign"
msgstr "指定"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:62
msgid "Assigns selected vertices to this hook."
msgstr "指定选择好的顶点到该挂钩。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:66
msgid ""
"The Hook Modifier stores vertex indices from the original mesh to determine "
"what to affect. This means that modifiers that generate geometry, like "
"*Subdivision Surface*, should always be put **after** the *Hook* one in the "
"stack. Otherwise, the generated geometry will be left out of the hook's "
"influence."
msgstr ""
"挂钩修改器保存了来自原始网格的顶点索引以确定影响哪些顶点。这意味着，产生新的几"
"何形状的修改器（例如细分修改器），在堆栈中应该在钩挂修改器 **之后** 应用，否则"
"产生的几何形状将不会受挂钩操作的影响。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:73
msgid "Example"
msgstr "例子"

#: ../../manual/modeling/modifiers/deform/hooks.rst:78
msgid "Empty used as Hook to deform a subdivided cube."
msgstr "用空物体做为挂钩来使细分的立方体变形。"
